  "title" : "Jackson - Deserialize using generic class",
  "body" : "<p>I have a json string, which I should deSerialize to the following class</p>\n\n<pre><code>class Data &lt;T&gt; {\n    int found;\n    Class&lt;T&gt; hits\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>How do I do it?\nThis is the usual way</p>\n\n<pre><code>mapper.readValue(jsonString, Data.class);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>But how do I mention what T stands for?</p>\n"
}